sentences.english: Next year has been designated as the Year of China-Pakistan Friendship. A number of exchange activities will be held.
sentences.chinese: 明年是“中巴友好年”，雙方將舉辦一系列交流活動。

sentences.english: This year marks the 60th anniversary of the China-Pakistan relationship.
China and Pakistan have a lustily growing trade relationship, worth almost $9 billion last year.
sentences.chinese: 中巴貿易關係增長堅挺，去年約有90億的貿易值。

sentences.english: Hu said that both countries are close, friendly neighbors.
sentences.chinese: 胡錦濤說，中巴兩國是親密友好的鄰邦。

sentences.english: Facts have proven that Pakistan and China are true friends sharing weal and woe.
sentences.chinese: 事實證明，中巴是患難與共的真正朋友。

sentences.english: Hu pointed out that this year marks the 55th anniversary of the establishment of diplomatic ties between both countries.
sentences.chinese: 胡錦濤指出，今年是中巴建交55週年。

sentences.english: The first feeder liner jointly devloped by China and Brazil has come off the assembling line and gone through its trial flight successfully.
sentences.chinese: 中巴合作生產的首架支線飛機已下線並試飛成功。

sentences.english: Liang introduced the steady progress of China-Pakistan economic and trade cooperation.
sentences.chinese: 梁文洮介紹說，中巴經貿合作穩步發展。

sentences.english: Zeng made highly positive comments on the development of bilateral relations.
sentences.chinese: 曾慶紅高度評價中巴關係發展。
艾倫向他的中巴車跑去。

sentences.english: To maintain and develop the overall friendly relations between China and Pakistan will benefit not only our present generations but also future generations.
sentences.chinese: 維護和發展好中巴全面友好關係功在當代，利在千秋。

sentences.english: Thirdly, Sino-Pakistani relations are facing up challenges in new era.
sentences.chinese: 新時期中巴關係面臨的挑戰。

sentences.english: Please brief us on the visit as well as China-Pakistan relations.
sentences.chinese: 請介紹此訪相關情況及中巴關係。

sentences.english: China-Pakistan relations are as firm as a rock and have withstood the tests of time.
sentences.chinese: 中巴關係堅如磐石，歷久彌新。
